Others: Dalton Knecht scored 10 points, dished one assist and committed one turnover.
He had three personal fouls in his 20:10 minutes of action.
Knecht shot 4 of 7, including 2 of 5 from deep.
Knecht received another nine minutes of action in the second half and scored only three points.
His stock within the Lakers staff is steadily rising because of his gravity on offense and serviceable defense.
He's also looked comfortable for someone only in his rookie season.
It was expected from him, considering he was viewed as a polished prospect compared to his draft mates after spending four years in college.
